width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>PrizmClaw 管理台</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"app-shell\">\n      <header class=\"app-header\">\n        <div>\n          <h1>PrizmClaw 管理台</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">聊天、截图、系统命令执行</p>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"status\" class=\"status\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\">就绪</div>\n      </header>\n\n      <!-- CONFIG PANEL (lines 19-31) — TARGET FOR COLLAPSIBLE CHANGE -->\n      <section class=\"panel config-panel\">\n        <h2>连接设置</h2>\n        <div class=\"form-grid\">\n          <label>\n            API Base URL（可选）\n            <input id=\"baseUrlInput\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"留空表示同源，例如 http://127.0.0.1:3000\" />\n          </label>\n          <label>\n            Session ID\n            <input id=\"sessionIdInput\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"默认自动生成，可手动修改\" />\n          </label>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n      <!-- ... rest of panels ... -->\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n```\n\n### public/styles.css (788 lines) — key relevant rules\n\n```css\n.panel {\n  background: var(--panel);\n  border: 1px solid var(--line);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  padding: 14px;\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(31, 38, 51, 0.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(31, 38, 51, 0.04);\n}\n\n.form-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));\n  gap: 12px;\n}\n```\n\n## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo tests exist for public/ static assets (HTML/CSS). Test suite: `node --test tests/**/*.test.js`\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"content":[{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01Cyrvke6r8i68BmXTvLmZJo","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/040-web-collapsible-config-panel/plan.md","content":"# Plan — F-040: Web Collapsible Config Panel\n\n## Key Components\n\n- **HTML**: Replace `<section class=\"panel config-panel\">` with `<details>/<summary>` pattern\n- **CSS**: Style `details.config-panel` and `details.config-panel > summary` to match panel design\n\n## Approach\n\nUse native HTML `<details>`/`<summary>` elements — zero JS required, browser-native collapsing.\nThe `open` attribute on `<details>` makes it expanded by default.\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n- `public/index.html` — wrap config-panel content in `<details open>`/`<summary>`\n- `public/styles.css` — add styles for `details.config-panel` and its summary element\n\n## Data Flow\n\nNo data flow changes — purely presentational HTML/CSS.\n\n## Tasks\n\n- [ ] Task 1: Update `public/index.html` — replace config-panel `<section>` with `<details open>`/`<summary>`\n- [ ] Task 2: Update `public/styles.css` — add collapsible panel styles (summary cursor, marker, padding)\n- [ ] Task 3: Verify acceptance criteria mentally and run test suite\n"},"name":"Write","type":"tool_use"}],"id":"req_vrtx_011CZKAEd4TEYPV78PmZwVkc","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":1408,"output_tokens":24,"cache_read_input_tokens":52619},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5f55fa62-170a-4aab-9c7e-d8b931fa4810","uuid":"a5d2633c-7ff5-4493-85b9-fb38f19707db"}
