s.css` — add collapsible panel styles (summary cursor, marker, padding)","-- [ ] Task 3: Verify acceptance criteria mentally and run test suite","+- [x] Task 3: Verify acceptance criteria mentally and run test suite"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
